text: Anachis vermiculucostata is a species of sea snail in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==References== * Monsecour, K. & Monsecour, D., 2009. - A new species of Anachis (Gastropoda: Neogastropoda: Columbellidae) from the Philippines. title: Anachis vermiculucostata
